I worked out the colours first, light blue (du) dark blue (se) yellow (xo, sho) red (fa or tha), then I worked out the shape, circle (wopi) pentagon (buvi) explosion thing (zeti) cross (gafi). I did not use any notes as I assumed that would be cheating ( I wouldn't have had time anyway)

I found naming the shapes easiest, the "fa and tha" and "xo and sho" were hardest
